'.\" -*- nroff -*-
.TH KAFS-FRONT 8 "2026-03-09" "kafs 0.2.3" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
kafs-front \- hotplug front supervisor for kafs-back process
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kafs-front
.RB [ --uds
.IR path ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B kafs-front
manages lifecycle of
.BR kafs-back (8)
for hotplug mode.
It performs handshake/session restore and restarts back process when requested.
.PP
The default UDS path is
.IR /tmp/kafs-hotplug.sock .
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR --uds " " <path>
Set hotplug UDS endpoint path.
.TP
.BR -h ", " --help
Show help and exit.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B KAFS_HOTPLUG_UDS
Default UDS path when
.B --uds
is not provided.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kafs (1),
.BR kafsctl (1),
.BR kafs-back (8)
.SH AUTHOR
kafs project.
